data.description: Two Story home in coveted Jack Britt School District, Windsong neighborhood off King Rd.  Spacious home has 4 bedrooms (2x master BR's- one Up and Downstairs), 3 full baths and 1 half with formals  House has natural gas fire place, water heater & Gas Pack.  Features eat-in kitchen, Study, Large Bonus room above the 2 car garage.  New Heat Pump being installed comes with a 10 year warranty. Master Bath Down Stairs has a large Jacuzzi Tub.  Spacious lot backs up to wooded area, did someone mention privacy!   Low County Taxes and Minutes for Stoney Piont Elementary and Jack Britt High School.    A must see!
